378
00:21:41,620 --> 00:21:43,520
 To je ta priča sa Davidom Reimerom

379
00:21:43,520 --> 00:21:47,740
 gdje se vršio taj eksperiment,

380
00:21:47,740 --> 00:21:50,820
 tako zvani John-John eksperiment,

381
00:21:50,820 --> 00:21:51,900
 gdje je on zapravo,

382
00:21:51,900 --> 00:21:53,720
 uzevši blizance,

383
00:21:53,720 --> 00:21:56,800
